title: One bedroom Fully Furnished unit utilities included
posting_body: One bedroom fully furnished luxury unit is a destination trailer which is approx 400 sq.
ft. Bigger and better than Tiny home living.
Because, this unit has loads of space and storage.
No Smoking/Vaping.
No Pets.
Located in a secluded; secure, quite rural location just 5 minutes to I-5 on ramps, and 10 minutes from downtown Olympia.
Turn key move-in.
Including: theater seating, a full entertainment system, HD TV, fireplace, 4 seat dinette, full size refrigerator, built in vacuum; all kitchen utensils.
Walk-in shower.
King size bed.
All Utilities included: cable TV, high speed internet, electricity, propane, water, and garbage service.
You supply linens.
Secure parking.
Single Occupancy $1400.
You have received a 5 star review on your property listing from a traveling professional!
Tenant review:  "After having my housing plans fall through, I was lucky enough to find this listing.
It’s hard to believe that I was living in an RV.
This was the fanciest RV I have seen, a fireplace, full kitchen and recliners, not to mention the nicely sized bathroom and king-sized bed.
As great as this place was the property and tenants were even better.
The property is fenced and gated, beautifully landscaped and the pony that lives on the property was a joy to watch.
The landlord is incredible, whatever you need.
Trash and recyclables area on property (neither the trash nor the pony EVER smelled bad)."
